
## HOW PSI LAB IS USED TO TRAIN PSI SOLDIERS ?

- psi lab facility that provides a service
- service is required to promote a unit to new class
- promotion requires either experience (type = 0) or transformation (type = 3) and it takes time e.g. 30 days
- this new class e.g. psionic allows to use specific items like psi amp
- also this class gives boost to magic skills, which other classes do not
- other magical classes could be created like cleric in other special facilities that would allow to use other special items like healing

